  <title translate="true">Constructors</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Constructors</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Smalltalk has no constructors. If you want to perform instance initialization, you can redefine the &quot;new&quot; class method to initialize the instance.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table rowcount="2" colcount="2" style="cell-padding:0px; cell-spacing:0px; border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#000000; border-style:solid;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:312px;">
          <para style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px;"><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">Java</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:312px;">
          <para style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px;"><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">Smalltalk</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:312px;">
          <para style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px;"><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">Reservation()</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">{</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">startTime = </text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">new GregorianCalendar().getTime();</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">endTime =</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">new GregorianCalendar().getTime();</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">}</text></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; width:312px;">
          <para style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px;"><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">Reservation class method:</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">new</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">^super new initialize</text><br/><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">Reservation instance method:</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">initialize</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">startTime := Timestamp now.</text><br/><text style="font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;; font-size:9pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">endTime := Timestamp now</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
